snippet.title: 【趙雲傳重製版】Three Kingdoms Zhao Yun demo available now#steamnextfest
snippet.description:
Three Kingdoms Zhao Yun demo in Steam Next Fest2023.
Here you could experience part of the fourth chapter. 
Full version coming to Steam: Q3 2023

Steam2023新品節demo內容速遞！
正式版登陸時間：2023年 第三季度

Getting wishlists greatly helps us to be more visible in the Steam Fest which in turn contributes a lot to the game’s success when it launches. 
◆ Wishlist：https://store.steampowered.com/app/2201710/Three_Kingdoms_Zhao_Yun/

✉️If you have other questions, do not hesitate to raise them after joining our Discord and Reddit!
◆ Discord: https://discord.gg/cgMMR6BgrF
◆ Reddit: https://new.reddit.com/r/ThreeKingdomsZhaoYun

👀For all the latest info, follow us on social media:
◆Twitter:  https://twitter.com/etimestudio
